## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-159"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> nie powinna być wywoływana przed zakończeniem ładowania dokumentu, który implementuje on.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-159"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-160">Po zakończeniu ładowania dokumentu przez obsługi, można wykrywać <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> zdarzeń.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-160">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-161">Poniższy przykład przedstawia sposób wywołania funkcji skryptu w dokumentu z [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] aplikacji za pomocą <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-161">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-162">W tym przykładzie funkcja skryptu nie ma parametrów.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-162">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-163">Poniżej przedstawiono [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] dokument, który implementuje funkcję skryptów, które będą wywoływane z [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-163">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-164">Poniżej przedstawiono [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] wykonania wywołania funkcji skryptu w [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-164">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-172"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> nie powinna być wywoływana przed zakończeniem ładowania dokumentu, który implementuje on.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-172"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-173">Po zakończeniu ładowania dokumentu przez obsługi, można wykrywać <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> zdarzeń.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-173">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-174">Jeśli wartości za mało parametrów nie są przekazywane do skryptu, który jest, parametry, które nie są przekazywane wartości będzie mieć niezdefiniowana wartość.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-174">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-175">W przypadku przekazania za dużo wartości parametrów, nadmiarowe wartości są ignorowane.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-175">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-176">Poniższy przykład przedstawia sposób wywołania funkcji skryptu w dokumencie z aplikacji przy użyciu <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-176">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-177">W tym przykładzie skrypt funkcje wymagane parametry.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-177">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-178">Poniżej przedstawiono dokumentu, który implementuje funkcje skryptu, które będą wywoływane z [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-178">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-179">Poniżej przedstawiono [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementacji, aby wywołać skrypt działa w [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-179">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-193">Wywoływanie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> ma ten sam efekt co ustawienie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> właściwości.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-193">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> jest używany z poziomu znacznika przez deweloperów, którzy chcą deklaratywnie określić początkowy dokumentu, który <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> przechodzi do kiedy <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> został zainicjowany.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-195">Użyj <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> metodę, aby przejść do adresu URL, który może zawierać znaki specjalne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-195">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-196">Użyj <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> metody, aby przejść do <xref:System.Uri> nie zawiera znaki specjalne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-197">Poniższy przykład przedstawia użycie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> można przejść do dokumentu za pomocą <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> metody.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-197">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-215">Użyj <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> metodę, aby przejść do adresu URL, który może zawierać znaki specjalne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-215">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-216">Użyj <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> metody, aby przejść do <xref:System.Uri> nie zawiera znaki specjalne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-216">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-217">Poniższy przykład przedstawia sposób przejdź do dokumentu i otwórz go w nowym oknie przeglądarki, określając "o: puste" docelowej.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-217">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-226">Jeśli `stream` parametr jest `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> przechodzi do pusty dokument ("o: puste").</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-226">If the `stream` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-227">Jeśli parametr strumienia nie jest w prawidłowym [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, będzie on wyświetlany jako zwykły tekst.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-227">If the stream parameter is not in a valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-228">Po nawigacji <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> będzie `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-228">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e68e-229">Poniższy przykład pokazuje, jak można przejść do strumienia, który zawiera dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e68e-229">The following example shows how to navigate to a stream that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStreamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a stream  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream source = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  
  // Navigate to HTML document stream  
  this.webBrowser.NavigateToStream(source);  
}  
```

  
  
